    "Drag mod folders or downloaded ZIP archives into the window. Seed Box previews every install before touching anything, archives whatever it replaces, and keeps your settings when a mod is updated.": {
      "comment": "Help window content.",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ziehe Mod-Ordner oder heruntergeladene ZIP-Archive ins Fenster. Seed Box zeigt jede Installation als Vorschau an, bevor etwas verändert wird, archiviert alles, was ersetzt wird, und behält deine Einstellungen bei Mod-Updates."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Drag mod folders or downloaded ZIP archives into the window. Seed Box previews every install before touching anything, archives whatever it replaces, and keeps your settings when a mod is updated."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Arrastra carpetas de mods o archivos ZIP descargados a la ventana. Seed Box muestra una vista previa de cada instalación antes de tocar nada, archiva lo que reemplaza y conserva tus ajustes cuando un mod se actualiza."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Glissez des dossiers de mods ou des archives ZIP téléchargées dans la fenêtre. Seed Box prévisualise chaque installation avant de toucher quoi que ce soit, archive ce qu'il remplace et conserve vos réglages lors des mises à jour."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Trascina cartelle di mod o archivi ZIP scaricati nella finestra. Seed Box mostra un'anteprima di ogni installazione prima di toccare qualsiasi cosa, archivia ciò che sostituisce e conserva le impostazioni quando una mod viene aggiornata."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "MODフォルダやダウンロードしたZIPアーカイブをウインドウにドラッグします。Seed Boxは何かを変更する前に必ずインストール内容をプレビューし、置き換えたものをアーカイブし、MODの更新時には設定を引き継ぎます。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "모드 폴더나 다운로드한 ZIP 파일을 창으로 드래그하세요. Seed Box는 변경 전에 모든 설치를 미리 보여주고, 교체되는 것은 보관하며, 모드 업데이트 시 설정을 유지합니다."
          }
        },
        "nl": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Sleep mod-mappen of gedownloade ZIP-archieven naar het venster. Seed Box toont een voorbeeld van elke installatie voordat er iets wordt aangepast, archiveert wat wordt vervangen en behoudt je instellingen bij een mod-update."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Arraste pastas de mods ou arquivos ZIP baixados para a janela. O Seed Box mostra uma prévia de cada instalação antes de tocar em qualquer coisa, arquiva o que substitui e mantém suas configurações quando um mod é atualizado."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "将模组文件夹或下载的 ZIP 压缩包拖入窗口。Seed Box 会在做出任何更改前预览每次安装，归档被替换的内容，并在模组更新时保留你的设置。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
