    "Half of the suspect mods have been disabled. Launch Stardew Valley, check whether the problem still happens, then come back and choose below. Your previous mod states are restored when the search ends.": {
      "comment": "Label in the problem-mod search (bisection) sheet.",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Die Hälfte der verdächtigen Mods wurde deaktiviert. Starte Stardew Valley, prüfe, ob das Problem weiterhin auftritt, und wähle danach unten aus. Die vorherigen Mod-Zustände werden am Ende der Suche wiederhergestellt."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Half of the suspect mods have been disabled. Launch Stardew Valley, check whether the problem still happens, then come back and choose below. Your previous mod states are restored when the search ends."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Se ha desactivado la mitad de los mods sospechosos. Inicia Stardew Valley, comprueba si el problema persiste y luego vuelve y elige abajo. Los estados anteriores de tus mods se restauran al terminar la búsqueda."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "La moitié des mods suspects a été désactivée. Lancez Stardew Valley, vérifiez si le problème persiste, puis revenez choisir ci-dessous. Les états précédents de vos mods sont restaurés à la fin de la recherche."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Metà delle mod sospette è stata disattivata. Avvia Stardew Valley, verifica se il problema persiste, poi torna e scegli qui sotto. Gli stati precedenti delle mod vengono ripristinati al termine della ricerca."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "疑わしいMODの半分が無効になりました。Stardew Valleyを起動して問題がまだ起こるか確認し、戻ってきて下から選択してください。検索が終了すると、以前のMODの状態が復元されます。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "의심되는 모드의 절반이 비활성화되었습니다. Stardew Valley를 실행하여 문제가 계속 발생하는지 확인한 후 돌아와서 아래에서 선택하세요. 검색이 끝나면 이전 모드 상태가 복원됩니다."
          }
        },
        "nl": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "De helft van de verdachte mods is uitgeschakeld. Start Stardew Valley, controleer of het probleem zich nog voordoet en kies daarna hieronder. De vorige modstatussen worden hersteld wanneer de zoekopdracht eindigt."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Metade dos mods suspeitos foi desativada. Inicie o Stardew Valley, verifique se o problema ainda ocorre e depois volte e escolha abaixo. Os estados anteriores dos seus mods são restaurados quando a busca termina."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "一半可疑模组已被停用。请启动星露谷物语，检查问题是否仍然出现，然后回来在下方选择。搜索结束后将恢复之前的模组状态。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
