    },
    "Seed Box manages the mods in your Stardew Valley Mods folder. Choose the folder once and Seed Box keeps watch over it — even changes made outside the app are noticed.": {
      "comment": "Help window content.",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Seed Box verwaltet die Mods in deinem Stardew-Valley-Mods-Ordner. Wähle den Ordner einmal aus, und Seed Box behält ihn im Blick — auch Änderungen außerhalb der App werden bemerkt."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Seed Box manages the mods in your Stardew Valley Mods folder. Choose the folder once and Seed Box keeps watch over it — even changes made outside the app are noticed."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Seed Box gestiona los mods de tu carpeta Mods de Stardew Valley. Elige la carpeta una vez y Seed Box la vigilará; incluso nota los cambios hechos fuera de la app."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Seed Box gère les mods de votre dossier Mods de Stardew Valley. Choisissez le dossier une fois et Seed Box le surveille — même les changements faits hors de l'app sont remarqués."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Seed Box gestisce le mod nella cartella Mods di Stardew Valley. Scegli la cartella una volta e Seed Box la terrà d'occhio: nota anche le modifiche fatte fuori dall'app."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Seed BoxはStardew ValleyのModsフォルダ内のMODを管理します。フォルダを一度選択すれば、Seed Boxが見守ります。アプリ外での変更にも気づきます。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Seed Box는 Stardew Valley의 Mods 폴더에 있는 모드를 관리합니다. 폴더를 한 번 선택하면 Seed Box가 계속 지켜봅니다. 앱 밖에서 일어난 변경도 알아차립니다."
          }
        },
        "nl": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Seed Box beheert de mods in je Stardew Valley Mods-map. Kies de map één keer en Seed Box houdt deze in de gaten — zelfs wijzigingen buiten de app worden opgemerkt."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "O Seed Box gerencia os mods da sua pasta Mods do Stardew Valley. Escolha a pasta uma vez e o Seed Box ficará de olho nela — até mudanças feitas fora do app são percebidas."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Seed Box 管理 Stardew Valley Mods 文件夹中的模组。只需选择一次文件夹，Seed Box 就会持续关注它——即使是在应用外做出的更改也会被注意到。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Seed Box manages this Mods folder directly.": {
      "comment": "Message about the Stardew Valley Mods folder managed by Seed Box.",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
